00:00:02.400 --> 00:00:09.100
Mini Orange Cheesecake

00:00:09.100 --> 00:00:14.500
Equipment: 8 tart tins of 8cm diameter

00:00:14.500 --> 00:00:17.700
Ingredients for biscuit base

00:00:17.700 --> 00:00:21.400
250 g digestive biscuits

00:00:21.400 --> 00:00:25.700
125 g (Â½ cup) butter, melted

00:00:25.700 --> 00:00:26.900
Ingredients for the filling

00:00:26.900 --> 00:00:31.200
2 oranges, cut into segments

00:00:31.200 --> 00:00:35.300
250 g (1 cup) cream cheese

00:00:35.300 --> 00:00:38.400
1 tsp orange zest

00:00:38.400 --> 00:00:43.700
180 g (2/3 cup) sweet condensed milk

00:00:43.700 --> 00:00:46.100
2 tbsp lemon juice

00:00:46.100 --> 00:00:48.700
1 tbsp orange juice

00:00:48.700 --> 00:00:49.800
Ingredients for decoration

00:00:49.800 --> 00:00:52.200
8 orange segments

00:00:52.200 --> 00:00:55.500
Directions for the biscuit base

00:00:55.500 --> 00:00:59.700
Grease 8 mini tart tins.

00:00:59.700 --> 00:01:07.900
Place the biscuits in a food processor and pulse until finely crushed. 

00:01:07.900 --> 00:01:23.000
Transfer to a bowl and pour the melted butter over then stir to combine and form a paste.

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:39.300
Divide the biscuit base among the 8 tart tins and press to form an even layer. Place the tart tins in the fridge.

00:01:39.300 --> 00:01:40.400
Directions for the filling

00:01:40.400 --> 00:01:50.500
Cut the orange into segments, without any skin. Reserve 8 pieces and chop the rest into small dices.

00:01:50.500 --> 00:02:02.000
Using an electric whisk beat together the cream cheese and lemon zest until smooth.

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:11.800
Gradually add the sweet condensed milk while beating along with the orange and lemon juice.

00:02:11.800 --> 00:02:17.700
Keep beating for about 5 minutes until the mixture is smooth and thick.

00:02:17.700 --> 00:02:26.500
Stir in the chopped oranges and spoon the filling into the tart tins. 

00:02:26.500 --> 00:02:29.300
Chill overnight in the fridge.

00:02:29.300 --> 00:02:31.400
Decorate the mini cheesecakes

00:02:31.400 --> 00:02:35.200
Garnish the top of each cheesecake tartlet with 1 orange segments.

